---
---
<section class="section patents-section" id="patents">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="patents-wrapper reveal">
      <div class="patents-info">
        <h2 class="section-title">Global <span class="text-gradient">Patents</span></h2>
        <p class="section-subtitle">Pioneering intellectual property in the field of intelligent neuro-rehabilitation and functional modeling.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="patents-grid">
        <div class="patent-card">
          <div class="patent-id">NO. 201941038618</div>
          <h4 class="patent-name">Advanced Neuro Rehabilitation Curriculum</h4>
          <p class="patent-meta">A Novel and Robust Framework for clinical excellence.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="patent-card">
          <div class="patent-id">NO. 202241067553</div>
          <h4 class="patent-name">Assessment of Functional Brain Circuits</h4>
          <p class="patent-meta">System and Methodology for predicting independence.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="patent-card">
          <div class="patent-id">NO. 202441038844</div>
          <h4 class="patent-name">Intelligent Rehab Environment</h4>
          <p class="patent-meta">Advancing Functional Neurosciences with IoMT tech.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="patent-card">
          <div class="patent-id">NO. 202441038858</div>
          <h4 class="patent-name">Multidimensional Prognostic Modelling</h4>
          <p class="patent-meta">Optimizing Functional Neurosciences outcomes.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .patents-section {
    background: #ffffff;
  }

  .patents-wrapper {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 0.8fr 1.2fr;
    gap: 80px;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .patents-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 24px;
  }

  .patent-card {
    background: var(--bg-slate);
    padding: 32px;
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    transition: var(--transition-smooth);
    border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
  }

  .patent-card:hover {
    background: white;
    border-color: var(--primary-color);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
    transform: translateY(-5px);
  }

  .patent-id {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--primary-color);
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    opacity: 0.8;
  }

  .patent-name {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--text-main);
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  .patent-meta {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-style: italic;
  }

  @media (max-width: 992px) {
    .patents-wrapper {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .patents-info {
        margin-bottom: 40px;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .patents-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
